+- Global and local paths are agent-specific:
+  - Claude Code: `~/.claude/skills/rhei-<skill>/` and `~/.claude/CLAUDE.md`;
+    local `.claude/skills/rhei-<skill>/` and `.claude/CLAUDE.md`.
