+### 5. Skill Installation Command And Agent-Specific Paths
+
+Normative claims:
+
+- `rhei install-skills` usage accepts `--agent <NAME>`, `--local`, `--link`,
+  `--uninstall`, `--dry-run`, and `--skills <LIST>`.
+- Supported agents are `claude-code`, `cursor`, `windsurf`, `copilot`,
